{"tid":1305232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO平權都唔會放棄香港！","createTime":"2019-07-10T20:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T13:07:50.000Z","uid":267304,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f94a298f2f4cab82ce4d62c38fee41f68cdb440","tid":1305232,"uid":267304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:48:19.000Z","msg":"睇完BNO個post，好想講即使BNO平左權都好，我都唔會放棄香港同班戰友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然會有手足覺得平左權你班撚屌仲會留係到磨爛蓆咩...無錯，我就係會留係到同大家磨到呢塊蓆變粉個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港點都係我既家！我相信有左BNO平權班手足仲大機會會進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋最重點：英國佬撚有咁順攤咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打少陣丁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3c191640bba66a2f3a649778f6800f14be6f7b","tid":1305232,"uid":267304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:01:33.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"96ad63ffce2e4ebaa7a42af364896af35844c615","tid":1305232,"uid":267304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:01:46.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"3a319d252ebca88de0c622b4b35681b747780eae","tid":1305232,"uid":267304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:01:56.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"10285df6a9491f342095c1a32f7bfbc589428535","tid":1305232,"uid":267304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:02:06.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"ace741da33cefb61e74792f9fe2baee9c8a510d2","tid":1305232,"uid":267304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:02:16.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"53f0bf4ca18120d72d499ca0d6c9c55fe9b12619","tid":1305232,"uid":267304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:02:26.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"93404b7c638321a2ccd41626276b5f3a690dbcec","tid":1305232,"uid":267304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r